high_descs: Turn left to exit the room and walk to the bedroom on the left to reach the bed.
Pick up the yellow cloth from the bed.
Turn around to exit the bedroom and walk left to reach the bathroom sink.
Wash the cloth in the sink and take it out.
Turn left and walk to the shelf next to the couch.
Put the cloth in the shelf.
anns.task_desc: Put the washed cloth in the bottom shelf.

high_descs: Turn left and leave the room on your right, then turn left and head to the bed on your right.
Pick the cloth from the bed.
Turn right and head to the sink on your left.
Put the cloth in the sink, rinse it off, and pick it back up.
Turn left, then head right to the shelf on your left.
Place the cloth in the shelf.
anns.task_desc: Place the cloth in the shelf.

high_descs: Turn left to head out of the kitchen and turn left to reach the bedroom and head to the bed.
Pick up the cloth from the bed.
Turn around to head out of the bedroom and walk across the room and turn left to reach the bathroom sink on the left.
Wash the cloth in the sink and take it out.
Turn left to exit the bathroom and turn right to reach the shelf.
Put the cloth in the shelf.
anns.task_desc: Put the washed cloth in the shelf.
